K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n#科興​ #疫苗​ #Sinovac​<br />\n00:00​ 香港應該停打科興疫苗 <br />\n00:47​ 科興疫苗嘅副作用點會係呼吸困難<br />\n03:35​ 了解三大類型疫苗：mRNA、腺病毒同滅活<br />\n10:35​ 點解德美兩國由mRNA開始研究<br />\n20:31​ 應該停打科興疫苗直至有研究結果為止<br />\n<br />\n#林鄭月娥​ #BioNTech​ #Moderna​ #AstraZeneca​ #評論​ #StayHome​ #WithMe​ #跟我一樣​ #宅在家​<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2F&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiukyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=51d095f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"20:31​ 應該停打科興疫苗直至有研究結果為止<br />\n<br />\n科興第三期臨牀研究一早出左<br />\n世柒點搞架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔出第三期點批呀"},{"pid":"eb4f707ba8b01e26f47912d51698e7155cb9f6d4","tid":2430662,"uid":16086,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"停打係冇錯<br />\n<br />\n不過依條友依然係垃圾"},{"pid":"26ac454df48e8dd4c335ebcaded22885b02b740c","tid":2430662,"uid":78519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:22:02.000Z","msg":"劉澤星：科興第三期數據未刊登期刊但委員會無降低標準<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府疫苗顧問專家委員會昨日開會通過向政府建議批准緊急使用科興疫苗。委員會召集人劉澤星在本台節目《千禧年代》表示， <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">雖然科興第三期研究數據未在醫學期刊刊登</span></span>，但委員會沒有降低標準，甚至要求更高。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575999-20210217.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575999-20210217.htm&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiukyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=297ecc0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575999-20210217.htm&h=9bb87013\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575999-20210217.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又有柒頭叻唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃生係話科興仲未起醫學期刊刊登第三期研究數據啊<br />\n<br />\n依家黃生叫科興快啲起醫學期刊刊登第三期研究數據啊"},{"pid":"d443da6abc39afb3133